# PyEncode generate_figures.py update — adds POPCOUNT, STAIRCASE, TENSOR,
# POLYNOMIAL to the per-pattern figures and gate count table; extends
# the scaling plot range to m = [6, 8, 10, 12, 16].
#
# POLYNOMIAL is deliberately NOT included in the scaling plot.  Its
# transpiled gate count at modest m has a large constant factor from
# multi-controlled phase corrections that obscures the clean
# poly(m)-vs-Qiskit story shown by the other eight patterns.  The
# gate count table shows POLYNOMIAL honestly at m=6 for d=1,2,3.
#
# PREREQUISITE: v1.3 patterns patch + bug-fix patch must already be applied.
#
# NOTE: Qiskit transpile at m=16 (N=65536) takes ~3 minutes.
#
# Apply with:  git apply pyencode_figures_update.diff
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

